|--------|------|-----------|
| `@dataclass` | `struct` with `#[derive(...)]` | Rust's derive macros provide similar functionality |
| `Optional[T]` | `Option<T>` | Rust's built-in option type |
| `List[str]` | `Vec<String>` | Owned, growable vector |
| Return `bool` for success/failure | Return `Result<(), Error>` | Explicit error handling with context |
| `datetime` | `chrono::DateTime<Local>` | Industry-standard date/time crate |
| Mutable default args `tags=None` | `Option<Vec<String>>` | Avoids Python's mutable default argument pitfall |
| Return task copy | Return `&Task` reference | Zero-copy, efficient borrowing |

